{
  "stem": "10272.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Instead of going to the army, this youngster has to-- has to be draft-- get draft-- get drafted and sign up.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They let me go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I came to an area.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They said, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You-- you sign up here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You have-- you have two days' time to get yourself a blanket, kit bag, and this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got a whole list of things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then you have to report to a place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They take you with a truck-- with a truck to a camp, to a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took me to a place called Yelshava.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yelshava, it was in Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But part of Slovakia, was-- Hungarian took over from Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this was a large camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that camp, they divided all these-- the people who were drafted to certain labor-- labor groups.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was put in a group of about 200 people, who were born in this age and this year when I was born.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they give us a crew of four people, Hungarian officers and sergeants.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They put us on a train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they dispatched us to a place called Tatabanya.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's not far from Budapest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There is a place where the next, Tatabanya, is a oil refinery place, oil refinery, and military camps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were-- they put us up in a-- in a barn to sleep, in a barn, and work on a-- on a construction site, helping manually with the bricks to supply for the brick layers.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was our job for, let's say, 5-6 months, we did this job.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had to get up at 6 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had at 7 o'clock was-- was a cup, we're standing in line for black coffee.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Either was black coffee or tea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a slice-- a good slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the only breakfast.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Lunch time we got some kind of a soup, a soup in a big pot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They brought there the pot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had-- and everybody had a [NON-ENGLISH], such a-- such a plate or something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They put this in soup.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The soup was not very good, some potato soup or something like this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They put in-- but it's not a real soup.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It didn't taste too good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we had to have something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we take it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were, after a month or two, we were so-- we were so good acquainted with the-- with the crew, that they would-- they would close their eyes.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They would look the other way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we would do our job a little faster, and have time to go around to the neighbors and ask for a few potatoes to give us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When we get home, we would have a few potatoes in the pockets.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For this, why-- why did they do it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because some of the guys from-- from our company, from our group, came from Budapest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Budapest, the parents were still-- they didn't take them away yet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even the Germans were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't touch yet, in Budapest, the Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they could get a day off, not officially.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would leave the camp, say, in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But by the evening, they should have-- they have to get back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took a train from Tatabanya to Budapest, take them half an hour, not a long way.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they would go there, sit and visit their parents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Came back with a package of wine, cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they would give for the officer, for the crew, cigarettes and wine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they were happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they would let them in turn to go home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that's why we had a good-- a good deal over there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They ?] [? wouldn't-- ?] It was hard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And for dinner, when you got home, we came home after 10 hours' work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we started 8 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By 6 o'clock, they would let us back home, 10 hours.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Came home, again there was a-- there was a kitchen there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not a real kitchen, but they were cooking there for us dinner.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And always these guys, we got provisions from Mauthausen, a place Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't know where this Mauthausen was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I heard that always the car.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "With the car, we had to go to Mauthausen and get us potatoes, and get us this and this, and all kind of things.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And these Jewish cooks, they were telling us where the-- from where these provisions are coming.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they would cook either a goulash from these potatoes, always some kind of meat was inside.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or-- or macaronis they would-- would give-- would cook for us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What else would you get?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some kind of a cooked meal you would have for dinner.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we would be able to make it and-- and work good.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
